    Men’s Shirts

    Top off any of your outfits with a comfortable, stylish, and versatile men’s shirt! From soft casual tees to sophisticated dress shirts, men’s tops can bring unmatched appeal to any of your daily outfit choices.

    With so many men’s shirts options out there, it might be best to start with simply figuring out the size of the shirt you need. This will allow you to have the information you need so you can be confident that you’re choosing the size that will fit you the best. Using the following information, you should be able to quickly and accurately discover what size is right for you whether dressing up or down.

    Casual shirt size chart
    Regular sizesNeckChestWaist

    M15"-15.5"38"-41"32"-35"
    L16"-16.5"42"-45"36"-39"

    Size chart is a general guide.

    Regular height: 5' 8" - 5' 11.5"
    Tall height: 6' - 6' 4"

    DRESS SHIRTS

    Most dress shirts are sold by neck size and sleeve length. Sleeve measurement determines the shirt's overall length to ensure a proper and comfortable fit. Dress shirts sold only by neck size still are designed proportional to the sleeve/body ratio. Check for additional sizing information on the product page for specific sleeve lengths for specific styles

    Suit Jackets, Sport Coats & Blazers

    Most men's suit jackets, sport coats and blazers are sold by chest size. Check your own measurements and look for more sizing information on the product page to determine your correct size. Jacket length corresponds to your overall height

    Short height: under 5' 8"
    Regular height: 5' 8" - 5' 11.5"
    Tall/Long height: 6' - 6' 4"

    Men’s shirt styles

    With your sizing information at hand, it’s now time to pick out that shirt that’s going to transform your look!

    Men’s dress shirts

    A crisp men’s dress shirt can up your look with ease. No matter if your shirt is a solid color or features a timeless pattern, it can offer impeccable style that’s ideal for work, a wedding, or any formal event.

    With easy-care, no-iron fabric, today’s dress shirts are even easier to clean, maintain, and keep looking fresh, wear after wear. And they also come in fits ranging from extra-slim to regular, so a perfect shirt for your body type and personal style is easy to find.

    Men’s casual button-down shirts

    For a bit more laid-back look, men’s button-down shirts provide the classic silhouette of a dress shirt, but a more casual look that can be worn untucked and to low-key events like neighborhood barbeques or happy hours.

    Casual button-downs also come in both short- and long-sleeve versions, so they can be worn all year round.

    Also in this category are Hawaiian shirts, casual tops with bright colors and floral patterns. These are great summertime tops that add a splash to any of your outfits.

    Men’s t-shirts

    For the ultimate in casual comfort, add a soft t-shirt to your wardrobe. Solid tees make for great layering pieces or for wearing simply on their own. Graphic tees add a punch of personality to your look, and can feature images or logos from your favorite movies, sports teams, music groups, and more.
